-- Project Euler 4: Largest palindrome from product of two 3-digit numbers
'is-6pal (
  dup dup 100000 div swap 10 mod eq
  over dup 10000 div 10 mod swap 100 mod 10 div eq and
  over dup 1000 div 10 mod swap 1000 mod 100 div eq and
) def

0 999 999
(
  'j let 'i let 'best let
  i j mul
  dup 100000 ge (is-6pal (best max) (drop best) if) (drop best) if
  i j dec dup i lt (drop dec 999) () if
  'j2 let 'i2 let 'best2 let
  best2 i2 j2
  i2 99 gt
) loop
drop drop
906609 eq assert
